name: Circular Toranj
description: Toranj or Citrus bergamia, the bergamot orange (pronounced /ˈbɜːrɡəmɒt/), is a fragrant citrus fruit the size of an orange, used in the center of persian carpets mostly. the Geometry and Philosophy of Toranj is the heart of several of my artworks its from a generative art project coded via Python - Pillow Graphed via Pytorch implementation of various GANs , using the Turtle module Created in Adobe Photoshop 2021
